  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical and radiological signs of coxarthritis

          -  Implantation of a total hip replacement indicated

          -  Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Osteoporosis

          -  Tumor

          -  Acute infection

          -  Higher grade congenital dysplasia of the hip

          -  Pregnancy
      </textblock>
